track.name: Good Morning Blues
comments: Excellent. So true that the white man's blues are totally different than the black man's blues.
Leadbelly is one of the Great.
Great Song! I love to whistle to blues.
Don't let the blues get ya...
thanks leadbelly, I finally figured out what's wrong with me
I AM that white man that had the Blues. SING IT LEADBELLY.
leadbelly with his rock n roll riff

Lead Belly... a common side affect of eating blues ridden bread.  Unfortunately this affliction is common throughout the aging blues artist community, but for just a few dollars you can sponsor a blues musician and help to find a cure for this ailment.  Just pennies a day...
I get this song stuck in my head all the time. Such a great tune.
blues all in my bread (like some mold o somethin') - the intro takes the cake -
Leadbelly is to blues, what Cash is to country and Reinhardt is to jazz....
